      span.glyphicon.glyphicon-menu-hamburger(aria-hidden='true')
  .main-content
    .container-fluid
      .row
        .col-md-4.hidden-sm.hidden-xs.fixedthing
          .panel.panel-default.section(id='main-menu')
            h1.resizable.text-center Katie & Kyle
            br
            h3.resizable.text-center(id='menu-date') July 09, 2016
            h2.resizable.text-center(id='menu-location') Morton, Illinois
            br
            h4.resizable.text-center(id='menu-paragraph')  welcome to our wedding website!
            hr.resizable-hr
            ul
              li.h2.menu-link
                a.resizable(id='home-link' href='#' ng-click='getHome()') Home
              li.h2.menu-link
                a.resizable(id='out-story-link' href='#' ng-click='getOurStory()') Our Story
              li.h2.menu-link
                a.resizable( id='wedding-party-link' href='#' ng-click='getWeddingParty()') Wedding Party
              li.h2.menu-link
                a.resizable(id='wedding-link' href='#' ng-click='getTheWedding()') The Wedding
              li.h2.menu-link
                a.resizable(id='travel-link' href='#' ng-click='getTravel()') Travel and Accommodations
              li.h2.menu-link
                a.resizable(id='song-link' href='#' ng-click='getSong()') Song Requests
              li.h2.menu-link
                a.resizable(id='registry-link' href='#' ng-click='getRegistry()') Registry
              li.h2.menu-link
                a.resizable(id='rsvp-link' href='#' ng-click='getRSVP()') RSVP
              li.h2.menu-link
                a.resizable(id='contact-link' href='#' ng-click='getContact()') Contact
              - if(admin == true)
                li.h2.menu-link
                  a.resizable(id='admin-link' href='#' ng-click='getAdmin()') Admin Tools
            hr.resizable-hr
            p.resizable.photoCred.text-center Photos courtesy of Meredith Washburn
            p.resizable.photoCred.text-center http://www.meredithwashburn.com


        // Main content ===============================================================
        .col-md-8.col-md-offset-4
          .section(id='main-content' )
            .home.article
              h1.content-title.text-center Count Down to Wedding
              hr
              .row(id='#countDown')
                .col-xs-2.col-xs-offset-1
                  .countDown-label.text-center {months}
                  .panel.panel-default
                    .panel-body
                      h1.month.countDown-h1.text-center
                .col-xs-2
                  .countDown-label.text-center {days}
                  .panel.panel-default
                    .panel-body
                      h1.day.countDown-h1.text-center
                .col-xs-2
                  .countDown-label.text-center {hours}
                  .panel.panel-default
                    .panel-body
                      h1.hour.countDown-h1.text-center
                .col-xs-2
                  .countDown-label.text-center {minutes}
                  .panel.panel-default
                    .panel-body
                      h1.min.countDown-h1.text-center
                .col-xs-2
                  .countDown-label.text-center {seconds}
                  .panel.panel-default
                    .panel-body
                      h1.sec.countDown-h1.text-center
            .ourstory.article
              h1.content-title Our Story
              hr
              p Katie and Kyle started "dating" in jr. high on May 26th, 2008 during their 8th Grade trip to Washington D.C.&nbsp;
                img(id='firstPic' src='/images/ourstory/firstPic.JPG' height='200px' ng-click='picModal($event)')
                | Kyle was drawn to Katie's grace and poise when she walked into a sign while talking to him at the airport, and Katie was charmed when Kyle first texted her a poop emoji.
                | Their relationship continued to grow after starting high school. Together they stayed busy excelling in classes, playing sports, and&nbsp;
                img(id='prom' src='/images/ourstory/prom.jpg' height='200px' ng-click='picModal($event)')
                | volunteering. They also enjoyed playing together in orchestra and attending homecomings and proms. In 2012, Kyle and Katie graduated from Morton High School and parted ways as Kyle went to
                | Southern Illinois University in Carbondale, and Katie attended the University of Illinois in Urbana-Champaign. They have&nbsp;
                img(id='grad' src='images/ourstory/grad.JPG' height='200px' ng-click='picModal($event)')
                | maintained their long distance relationship with many skype dates and silly snapchats. In May of 2016, Kyle will graduate with a&nbsp;
                img(id='hiking' src='images/ourstory/hiking.JPG' height='200px' ng-click='picModal($event)')
                | bachelor's in Computer Science, and Katie will graduate with a bachelor's in Food Science and Human Nutrition with a concentration in Dietetics. Kyle plans to start working as a computer programmer,
                | while Katie will continue her education with graduate school and the dietetic internship, working toward becoming a dietitian. In their free time, the couple can be found outside hiking, camping, and
                | fishing, or inside cooking and watching Game of Thrones.
